{"type": "article", "id": 26967, "title": "MacBook 木质支架", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-18T07:23:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104155ghsGTyJcjEL5B8VI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这个来自 Nordic Appeal 的木质支架是专门为 MacBook 所设计的产品。在造型上采用了符合人体工程学的设计，大大减轻了普通的使用姿势对颈椎和手腕造成的负荷。如果平放在桌面上，支架下方还可以存放键盘和鼠标，让桌面显得更加整洁。除此之外，它还可以和木质旋钮搭配，变成一个让你可以站着办公的壁架，如果你对这个灵活的支架感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://nordicappeal.com/store/wall-desk/\">链接</a>购买，售价为 219.99 美元（不包括旋钮）。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104153vn7h3ieQ8PSG2VNm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104154HDlXLnSawNPCobAE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104154h3pjFIoCJfrUtW2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702104155lAnjpWGqxFH0EoTN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}